---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const products = [
  {
    name: 'Diffusion Plate Cleaning and Inspection Production Line',
    image: '/assets/img/automation/product-a.jpg',
    href: '/products/automation/product-a',
    desc: 'Integrated production line for diffusion plate cleaning, inspection, and continuous conveying with stable industrial workflow.'
  },
  {
    name: 'Robotic Automatic Loading and Unloading Cleaning Machine',
    image: '/assets/img/automation/product-b.jpg',
    href: '/products/automation/product-b',
    desc: 'Automated cleaning equipment with mechanical loading and unloading support for improved efficiency and reduced manual handling.'
  },
  {
    name: 'Polarizer Absorption Axis Angle Measuring System',
    image: '/assets/img/automation/product-c.jpg',
    href: '/products/automation/product-c',
    desc: 'High-precision measuring system for polarizer absorption axis angle, retardation, chromaticity, and transmittance analysis.'
  }
];
---

<Layout title="Industrial Automation Equipment | Display Manufacturing Lines | DGSDK"
  description="DGSDK industrial automation equipment: diffusion plate cleaning lines, robotic loading/unloading systems, and polarizer measurement instruments for display manufacturing.">
  <section
    class="products-hero"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18)), url('/assets/img/automation/automation-bg.png') center/cover no-repeat;"
  >
    <div class="container products-hero-inner">
      <span class="products-hero-kicker">DGSDK Product Portfolio</span>
      <h1>Automation Equipment</h1>
      <p>
        Efficient industrial automation solutions designed to improve production
        consistency, reduce labor costs, and support customized manufacturing needs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="products-overview-section">
    <div class="container products-overview-layout">
      <aside class="products-sidebar">
        <div class="products-sidebar-box">
          <h3>Browse Categories</h3>
          <a href="/products">All Products</a>
          <a href="/products/static-eliminator">Static Elimination Systems</a>
          <a href="/products/cleaning-machine">Cleaning Machine</a>
          <a href="/products/precision-machined-parts">Precision Machined Parts</a>
          <a href="/products/automation" class="active-category">Automation Equipment</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="products-main">
        <section class="apple-product-section">
          <div class="apple-card-grid">
            {products.map((product) => (
              <a href={product.href} class="apple-product-card">
                <img src={product.image} alt={product.name} loading="lazy" />

                <div class="apple-product-card-body">
                  <span class="apple-card-tag">Automation Equipment</span>
                  <h3>{product.name}</h3>
                  <p>{product.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="category-info-block">
          <h2>About DGSDK Automation Equipment</h2>
          <p>DGSDK designs and manufactures industrial automation equipment for electronics manufacturing, optical film processing, and display component production. Our automation systems integrate mechanical handling, precision cleaning, automated inspection, and measurement functions into streamlined production lines that reduce manual labor and improve output consistency.</p>
          <p>Each automation system is developed based on the specific production requirements of the customer, including throughput targets, material types, cleanroom compatibility, and integration with existing line equipment. Custom configurations are available for specialized applications.</p>

          <h3>Diffusion Plate Cleaning and Inspection Production Line</h3>
          <p>The <a href="/products/automation/product-a">diffusion plate cleaning and inspection production line</a> is an integrated system for LED and LCD display manufacturing. It combines surface cleaning, optical inspection, and continuous conveying into a single automated process. The integrated design eliminates manual handling between process steps, reducing contamination risk and improving throughput consistency.</p>
          <p>This system is used by display component manufacturers that require stable, repeatable cleaning and inspection results across high-volume production runs.</p>

          <h3>Robotic Loading and Unloading Cleaning Machine</h3>
          <p>The <a href="/products/automation/product-b">robotic automatic loading and unloading cleaning machine</a> uses mechanical arm handling to move substrates into and out of the cleaning station. This eliminates manual loading operations from the production line, reducing labor costs and minimizing handling-related defects. The robotic handling system is configurable for different substrate sizes and production speeds.</p>

          <h3>Polarizer Absorption Axis Angle Measuring System</h3>
          <p>The <a href="/products/automation/product-c">polarizer absorption axis angle measuring instrument</a> provides high-precision measurement of polarizer optical properties. It measures absorption axis angle, retardation value, chromaticity, and transmittance. These measurements are used for incoming quality control and in-process verification during polarizer manufacturing and lamination.</p>

          <h3>Automation Equipment Applications</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Diffusion plate cleaning and optical inspection production lines for display manufacturing</li>
            <li>Robotic loading and unloading cleaning systems for high-volume flat panel production</li>
            <li>Polarizer absorption axis angle measurement for quality control in polarizer processing</li>
            <li>Custom automation integration for electronics assembly and optical component manufacturing</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Contact us to discuss your automation requirements and receive a customized system proposal.</p>

          <h3>Industrial Automation for Display Manufacturing</h3>
          <p>Display component manufacturing presents specific automation challenges. Substrates such as diffusion plates, polarizer films, and backlight panels are large, fragile, and highly sensitive to surface contamination. Manual handling introduces particles, scratches, and static-related defects at every transfer point. Automated handling systems eliminate these risks by moving substrates through cleaning, inspection, and packaging stages without direct human contact.</p>
          <p>DGSDK's automation equipment is designed for the optical cleanliness requirements of display manufacturing environments. Conveyor speeds, handling pressures, and inspection parameters are configurable to match the specific substrate dimensions and throughput targets of each production line. Integration with existing line equipment is supported through customized mechanical and electrical interface design.</p>

          <h3>Custom Automation System Integration</h3>
          <p>Standard automation equipment covers the most common production configurations, but many electronics and display manufacturing lines require customized solutions. DGSDK develops custom automation systems based on detailed customer requirements including substrate type and dimensions, throughput target, cleanroom classification, integration points with upstream and downstream equipment, and operator interface preferences.</p>
          <p>Custom projects begin with a technical review of the production requirements. We provide a system design proposal covering the mechanical layout, process flow, control architecture, and estimated lead time before any commitment is made. This process ensures the delivered system meets the operational requirements of the production line from day one. Contact us to begin a technical review for your automation project.</p>

          <h3>Benefits of Automation Integration for Manufacturing</h3>
          <p>Automation enables consistent output across high-volume production runs. Each cycle repeats the same motion, force, and timing. This reduces defects from operator variation.</p>
          <p>Integrated solutions combine multiple process steps into one continuous line. Cleaning, inspection, and handling occur without manual transfer. This saves time and reduces contamination risk at each transfer point.</p>
          <p>Automation reduces costs over time. Labor requirements decrease. Scrap rates fall when inspection is automated and defects are caught early. Quality assurance becomes part of the production process rather than a separate step.</p>
          <p>Real time data from automated inspection systems gives production teams immediate feedback. Problems are identified as they occur. Operators can adjust process parameters without waiting for end-of-line sampling.</p>
          <p>DGSDK acts as a system integrator for customers who need a complete production line rather than individual machines. We design the mechanical layout, specify each process station, write the control software, and commission the system on-site. This single-source approach simplifies project management and accountability.</p>
          <p>Automation tools developed for display manufacturing must meet strict cleanliness standards. All mechanical components that contact substrates are designed for low particle generation. Control systems log process data at each station. This supports data integrity and traceability for quality assurance reporting. Contact us to discuss how automation integration can improve your production line efficiency and output quality.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>